{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id77cc37f7-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s460u–13"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"460u–13"},"text":"§ 460u–13.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Acquisition of area I–C; owner consent required","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id77cc37f8-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s460u–13/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The Secretary may acquire that portion of area I–C which is shaded on the map referred to in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s460u–3"},"text":"section 460u–3 of this title","children":[],"tail":", dated December 1980 and numbered 626–91014 only with the consent of the owner unless the present owner attempts to sell or otherwise dispose of such area."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id77cc37f9-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s460u–13/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The Secretary may acquire that portion of area IV–B in private ownership on the map referred to in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s460u"},"text":"section 460u of this title","children":[],"tail":" only with the consent of the owner: "},{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"Provided","children":[],"tail":", That the Secretary may acquire an agricultural easement should the owner change the use in existence as of "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-09-19"},"text":"September 19, 1986","children":[],"tail":", through eminent domain."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id77cc37fa-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/761/s13"},"text":"P